{"1":[[1068,1168,"Stop it!"],[1240,1416,"Come on, Sandy. No more kisses."],[1416,1512,"Wake up."],[1704,1804,"Who the hell are you?"],[1872,2032,"The First Lady of the country."],[2488,2640,"I know her well. And trust me,"],[2640,2760,"you're nothing like her."],[3132,3276,"I think the 15th cocktail"],[3276,3388,"was too much."],[4092,4340,"Richard! Bunny…"],[4548,4676,"Where are we?"],[4744,4836,"I don't—"],[5036,5140,"Who's this tramp?"],[5304,5456,"Why are you so close to her?"],[5560,5680,"Is she contagious?"],[5680,5780,"I'm not…"],[5900,5984,"but this mop…"],[6164,6340,"I can't guarantee anything."],[6576,6704,"Richard, call me"],[6704,6904,"when you figure this out."],[7300,7592,"No, no, no. Not so fast!"],[7592,7704,"Fess up. Who are you"],[7704,7864,"and what are you doing here?"],[7864,7956,"Back off!"],[8132,8344,"Meet the Harvard graduate—"],[8344,8528,"a Bachelor of Law—"],[8576,8672,"my son."],[8728,8904,"The future of our country lies"],[8904,9036,"with young men like him."],[9036,9188,"Yeah, hi. I'm Richard."],[9188,9340,"I'm a recent Harvard graduate."],[9340,9524,"And, yeah…"],[9524,9636,"So?"],[9636,9880,"So, you're the president's son?"]],"2":[[48,272,"So, you're the president's son?"],[272,404,"…and I also need a job."],[404,548,"So, if anyone's hiring"],[548,692,"and needs a lawyer…"],[756,900,"And you are a cleaner."],[972,1156,"Are we stating the obvious now?"],[1900,2000,"You like what you see?"],[2292,2392,"You want me to…"],[2464,2576,"drop this mannequin"],[2576,2720,"so you can get a better look?"],[2992,3160,"I'll take silence as a yes."],[3512,3612,"Well, then…"],[4168,4260,"Stop!"],[4388,4512,"Is that what they taught you"],[4512,4616,"at Harvard?"],[4680,4796,"What's your degree?"],[4796,4972,"Law? Then you should know"],[4972,5100,"this is harassment!"],[5148,5268,"And you have no right"],[5268,5388,"to even be here!"],[5540,5640,"Is that so?"],[5800,6016,"Well, I decide who has rights here."],[6168,6340,"Now, what's your best costume?"],[6996,7132,"Now, fetch me"],[7132,7340,"the best costume. Or I'll make sure"],[7340,7504,"you don't get hired as a cleaner"],[7504,7724,"anywhere. That's a promise."],[8176,8288,"Of course, sir."],[8392,8612,"I'll do my very best."]],"3":[[968,1068,"There was nothing else?"],[1200,1356,"I can offer you this mask as well."],[1420,1580,"It's part of the set."],[1672,1784,"You wouldn't want anyone"],[1784,1948,"recognizing you, would you?"],[2188,2436,"Not very presidential behavior!"],[2536,2636,"Your father's campaign"],[2636,2768,"is all about relating"],[2768,2920,"to regular people…"],[3236,3336,"Go to hell."],[3428,3660,"Hey! Aren't you gonna pay"],[3660,3788,"for the costume?"],[3860,3960,"Why don't you pay for it"],[3960,4044,"out of your pathetic…"],[4044,4176,"cleaner's salary?"]],"4":[[620,788,"How's the job hunt going?"],[960,1052,"Look, Dad."],[1052,1172,"You know I won't let you down."],[1220,1336,"I'll be the best lawyer"],[1336,1448,"in the country. But, you know,"],[1448,1548,"it takes time."],[1756,2000,"And we trust the father of this man"],[2000,2128,"to run the country?"],[2212,2312,"Thank goodness"],[2312,2396,"the presidential elections"],[2396,2524,"are around the corner."],[3140,3240,"What are you looking at?"],[4644,4804,"I'm waiting for an explanation."],[4908,5164,"Father, it's not what you think."],[5212,5432,"You've disappointed me. Pathetic."],[5432,5487,"Dad, I—"],[5498,5668,"Shut up!"],[5808,5936,"I don't care how…"],[5984,6068,"you'll fix this."],[6116,6264,"Now, get out!"],[6514,6531,"But I-"],[6532,6664,"I said get out!"],[7492,7620,"I hate you, you damn tramp!"],[8156,8332,"You will regret messing with me."]],"5":[[632,728,"You!"],[820,932,"Tried to profit off me huh,"],[980,1080,"you broke loser?"],[1200,1300,"Well, you didn't pay"],[1300,1392,"for the costume."],[1392,1608,"And my—what did you call it—"],[1608,1816,"\"pathetic salary\" wasn't enough."],[1864,1948,"And I got creative."],[2592,2712,"Who's supposed to clean it up?"],[2760,2904,"Well, between the two of us,"],[2904,3004,"the cleaner here is you."],[3004,3132,"So, take a guess."],[3260,3432,"Well, in that case,"],[3432,3576,"I might as well make a little money"],[3576,3668,"for myself."],[3716,3860,"How about that headline?"],[3860,4080,"\"President's Spoiled Son Attacks"],[4080,4296,"a Poor, Helpless Cleaner?\""],[4344,4444,"What?"],[4804,4976,"This time, we play by my rules."]],"6":[[912,1080,"Sir? Give us a comment."],[1080,1164,"What is happening"],[1164,1256,"between you two?"],[1256,1396,"I'm sorry so many people saw"],[1396,1520,"our role-playing games."],[1520,1720,"This is my girlfriend."],[1720,1848,"What?"],[1848,2020,"I told her it was a bit extravagant."],[2020,2220,"Us, the showroom, but—"],[2220,2364,"What's your name again?"],[2364,2464,"Mary."],[2464,2656,"But Mary insisted. And I'm weak"],[2656,2748,"when it comes to the love"],[2748,2844,"of my life."],[3020,3132,"Oh, great."],[3180,3308,"The president's son…"],[3308,3444,"What are you doing? Let me go."],[3444,3560,"Just be a good girl."],[3560,3696,"What a story. We'll see."],[3744,3828,"No, no, no."],[3828,3972,"No, no, no!"],[4040,4176,"Why does status matter?"],[4176,4260,"My father's campaign"],[4260,4404,"is all about regular people."],[4452,4506,"Right, babe?"],[4518,4632,"Not right, babe!"],[4632,4812,"Excuse us, but we've gotta go."],[4812,4896,"Yeah, sure. Thank you, sir."],[4896,4988,"Thank you."],[4988,5100,"I will kill you."],[5196,5288,"It was Elizabeth Skeeter"],[5288,5428,"for Breaking News Live."],[5492,5592,"Stay with us."]],"7":[[164,480,"Let me go. Let me go!"],[548,676,"Who do you think you are?"],[724,916,"I get it. You're in shock."],[916,1068,"That was the best kiss of your life,"],[1068,1240,"wasn't it? The best…"],[1240,1392,"and probably the only one."],[1392,1476,"Because who'd want"],[1476,1636,"a filthy cleaner?"],[2400,2624,"Good luck with your pathetic life!"],[3464,3600,"Vote for Michael Johnson."],[4728,4766,"Thank you."],[4792,4863,"The president's son,"],[4877,5012,"a young remarkable man,"],[5012,5228,"in love with an ordinary girl."],[5249,5425,"Could this be a new Cinderella story?"],[5467,5525,"We'll see."],[5548,5660,"Stay with us."],[5728,5812,"Sir? Give us a comment."],[5812,5896,"What's happening"],[5896,6008,"between you two?"],[6064,6200,"I'm sorry so many people saw"],[6200,6340,"our role-playing games."],[6388,6588,"This is my girlfriend."],[6588,6680,"What?"],[6680,6864,"I told her it was a bit extravagant."],[6864,7020,"Us, the showroom, but—"],[7020,7148,"What's your name again?"],[7148,7232,"Mary."],[7232,7408,"But Mary insisted. And I'm weak"],[7408,7520,"when it comes to the love"],[7520,7604,"of my life."],[7692,7776,"Nice!"],[7776,7904,"I'll destroy you both."]],"8":[[176,296,"I'll destroy you both."],[352,452,"Nice!"],[508,608,"The president's son"],[608,720,"and an ordinary cleaner."],[720,860,"What a story. We'll see."],[2968,3184,"Dad, I screwed up again."],[3256,3408,"You'd better hear it from me first."],[3508,3660,"You? Screwed up?"],[3784,3884,"Yes."],[4196,4340,"For the first time in my life,"],[4340,4432,"I'm proud of you."],[4764,4928,"Think, think, think!"],[5016,5168,"Think about what we can do next."],[5608,5692,"What did I pay"],[5692,5800,"your Harvard tuition for?"],[6124,6224,"What would you do without me,"],[6224,6336,"you useless brat?"],[6492,6700,"You'll have to marry the cleaner."],[6928,7020,"What?"]],"9":[[0,100,"Yes."],[336,512,"Everything must be perfect."],[560,668,"I know exactly what we need"],[668,776,"for the perfect picture."],[824,936,"Your mother's ring."],[992,1120,"Helen, get in here now!"],[1192,1384,"Dad, Mom will never agree to this."],[1384,1504,"That's a family heirloom."],[1612,1708,"Boys, can you…"],[1756,1908,"keep it down, please?"],[1908,2084,"My head is already pounding."],[2084,2188,"Gimme your hand."],[2304,2388,"Careful!"],[2668,2780,"Don't spill the wine."],[2780,2872,"So—"],[2872,3112,"So, is that all? Can I go now?"],[3112,3177,"Yeah, sure."],[3188,3400,"I have more important things to do."],[3400,3484,"Of course."],[3484,3664,"The bar won't empty itself."],[3756,3852,"You'd never guess"],[3852,3936,"you once dreamed of"],[3936,4052,"being First Lady."],[4460,4560,"By the way…"],[4652,4772,"You took the ring."],[4772,4996,"What's in it for me, Mr. President?"],[6240,6336,"What are you looking at?"],[6456,6540,"Turn around."],[8808,8900,"Thank you."],[10048,10176,"Don't disappoint me."],[10364,10476,"What if she says no?"],[10940,11040,"Then, son…"],[11124,11256,"you'll take her by force."]],"10":[[472,584,"Goodbye, Mr. Smith."],[584,720,"See you tomorrow."],[720,832,"Mary?"],[880,1000,"Yeah?"],[1256,1448,"There won't be a tomorrow."],[1504,1604,"You're fired."],[1716,1912,"But why? I—"],[1996,2220,"I'm employee of the month. Why?"],[2304,2428,"Mary, you know"],[2428,2548,"I've always liked you."],[2548,2648,"So, I'll be honest."],[2732,2844,"You've made some…"],[2960,3144,"powerful enemies in this town."],[3380,3524,"I shouldn't even be talking to you."],[3716,3844,"Leave."],[3948,4040,"Come back"],[4040,4168,"when you've settled things with…"],[4300,4400,"him."],[4672,4776,"Mr. Smith…"],[4776,4976,"I'm sorry, Mary. I'm sorry."],[4976,5208,"Mr. Smith, I'm begging you. No."],[5208,5400,"Please! But I need this job,"],[5400,5500,"and you know why!"],[5624,5661,"I'm sorry."],[5675,5876,"I'm just a small businessman. Sorry."],[5876,6004,"No, Mr. Smith. I'm begging you!"],[6004,6104,"Open the door!"],[6104,6272,"Mr. Smith, let's talk!"],[7036,7120,"Yeah?"],[7120,7248,"Mary, come immediately."],[7248,7360,"It's about your brother."]],"11":[[264,364,"Mary!"],[412,532,"Hey…"],[1484,1644,"Why do you look so sad?"],[1644,1804,"Did something happen at work?"],[2020,2188,"No, sweetheart. No."],[2352,2648,"I'm just… a bit tired."],[2704,2904,"Alright, you can discuss this later."],[2904,3136,"Run along. Your sister and I need"],[3136,3304,"to have a little chat."],[3872,4016,"This is for this month."],[4188,4336,"I would've brought it tomorrow,"],[4336,4436,"but your call…"],[4568,4744,"Sorry for the delay."],[4828,5004,"That's the thing."],[5004,5180,"Prices have gone up."],[5304,5480,"This is no longer enough."],[5480,5620,"You know about my situation."],[5620,5728,"I-I..."],[5784,5956,"I can't take my brother out of here."],[6004,6172,"Even though I dream of it."],[6280,6516,"I don't even have a proper place to live."],[6584,6800,"And I can't hear your excuses."],[6848,7004,"We've been over this before."],[7004,7088,"There are families"],[7088,7256,"willing to adopt Max."],[7304,7396,"If you can't afford"],[7396,7528,"to take care of him…"],[7612,7748,"you should give up custody."]],"12":[[0,112,"If you can't afford"],[112,240,"to take care of him…"],[332,468,"you should give up custody."],[764,856,"I'll get the money."],[920,1032,"Wise decision."],[2088,2200,"But this is impossible."],[2376,2476,"Oh, Mary…"],[2540,2692,"Don't act so innocent."],[2776,2860,"For the girlfriend"],[2860,3028,"of the president's son,"],[3028,3252,"nothing is impossible."],[3464,3712,"Jason, put down that cat!"],[3720,3842,"No!"],[3920,4040,"Old witch."],[4724,4816,"Hello."],[4816,4940,"So, baby, what's up?"],[5112,5212,"You."]],"13":[[64,164,"You."],[220,360,"You know, I've taken the initiative"],[360,444,"to make your life"],[444,552,"a little better."],[600,692,"I'll hunt you down"],[692,804,"and destroy you."],[804,932,"Not even your president daddy"],[932,1032,"will save you."],[1224,1368,"Why bother hunting me down?"],[1440,1524,"I'll be waiting for you"],[1524,1608,"at the Holton restaurant."],[1700,1828,"I'll send you the details."],[1876,2088,"What? You've lost your mind."],[2160,2384,"Relax. You need money, right?"],[2624,2760,"You don't have to answer."],[2760,2852,"I know you do."],[2936,3056,"And I need you."],[3104,3336,"So, I've got a business proposal"],[3336,3656,"for you. And wear something…"],[3656,3756,"presentable."],[3786,3900,"Presentable, presentable."],[3908,4105,"It's a very fancy place."],[4141,4280,"Kisses, darling."],[4588,4700,"You want war?"],[4816,4912,"You'll get it."],[4976,5076,"Sorry."],[6704,6952,"But someone's waiting for me!"],[6952,7064,"Ma'am, you're not allowed"],[7064,7252,"in here. This is a restaurant"],[7252,7372,"for respectable guests."],[7372,7620,"Him! Yes, him. The president's son"],[7620,7768,"is waiting for me! Hello, darling."]],"14":[[248,348,"No, no, no."],[444,548,"No, no, no."],[548,744,"Don't pretend you didn't want"],[744,880,"to see me here."],[972,1208,"So sorry. Sorry."],[1648,1888,"What? Like what you see?"],[2172,2420,"Am I presentable enough for you?"],[2420,2564,"I think I'm gonna be sick."],[2564,2732,"Oh, I'm so sorry, darling."],[2732,2900,"I didn't have much time"],[2900,3148,"to clean it up. Because, you know…"],[3232,3428,"I was too busy…"],[3476,3724,"getting fired because of you!"],[3724,3876,"Listen to me carefully."],[4024,4124,"What are you doing? Let go."],[4124,4220,"You're hurting me."]],"15":[[220,320,"What are you doing? Let go."],[320,416,"You're hurting me."],[416,528,"The more you fight…"],[612,740,"the longer I'll hold you."],[1036,1136,"What are you playing at?"],[1288,1456,"I could destroy you on a whim."],[1580,1732,"You pull one more stunt like this…"],[1816,1976,"and you'll regret ever crossing me again."],[2092,2192,"Got it?"],[3072,3156,"Take a look."],[4604,4756,"Um, this is—"],[4880,5024,"This must be a mistake."],[5108,5372,"It says I'm supposed to…"],[5472,5556,"marry you?"],[5752,5864,"It's not a mistake."],[6048,6256,"Just 'til my father's election is over."],[6320,6596,"You see… because of your little…"],[6596,6696,"dumpster stunt…"],[6824,6976,"I'm a bit dependent on you."],[7116,7284,"And who knew our love story"],[7284,7456,"would be such a hit with voters?"],[7556,7656,"But I can refuse."],[7656,7784,"You can't!"],[7888,8036,"Don't even dream of a quiet life"],[8036,8136,"if you do."],[8376,8608,"You see, the terms are simple."],[8692,8904,"We play a couple."],[8904,9024,"And if you perform well…"],[9120,9204,"you'll get to walk away"],[9204,9316,"with a hefty sum in the end."],[9760,9852,"Deal?"],[10248,10344,"Deal."],[10452,10552,"But…"],[10716,10948,"I need 50 grand up front."]],"16":[[508,628,"Did I say something funny?"],[724,808,"You could've asked for"],[808,892,"ten times more,"],[892,1016,"and I wouldn't have said no."],[1016,1216,"I don't need your dirty money."],[1400,1552,"Can I work while this…"],[1664,1784,"agreement lasts?"],[1896,2164,"No, you cannot. During the deal,"],[2164,2276,"no one will hire you."],[2324,2464,"Consider it my, uh…"],[2464,2632,"insurance that you won't bail."],[4880,5112,"And as the saying goes…"],[5320,5420,"Will you marry me?"],[5720,5952,"It's the worst proposal…"],[6000,6112,"I could ever imagine."],[6168,6268,"Good thing…"],[6372,6500,"I had my nails done."],[6628,6712,"Can we take a photo"],[6712,6824,"for Instagram?"],[6824,7056,"Happy couple and all of that?"],[7104,7188,"I'm not too thrilled"],[7188,7324,"about putting a family heirloom"],[7324,7456,"on some beggar."],[7588,7688,"I don't care."],[7964,8056,"Smile!"],[8156,8240,"I always imagined"],[8240,8496,"my fiancée would be classy…"],[8600,8736,"know her wines, and…"],[8880,9024,"have a sense of style."],[9428,9528,"Well…"],[9628,9756,"Why didn't you say so?"],[10136,10272,"I can arrange that."],[10584,10668,"Waiter!"]],"17":[[0,100,"What are you doing?"],[584,828,"I'll take the most expensive steak."],[828,920,"No."],[920,1132,"No, make that five steaks!"],[1132,1216,"Mary…"],[1216,1368,"And the priciest dishes"],[1368,1544,"from your starters, please."],[1652,1764,"Classy enough for you?"],[2144,2388,"And the ideal fiancée"],[2388,2548,"of the president's son"],[2548,2748,"should also know her wines."],[2748,2952,"Bring me the most expensive wine"],[2952,3036,"you have."],[3084,3184,"Two bottles!"],[3584,3768,"You can afford it. Right, darling?"],[3876,3976,"Anything else?"],[4268,4380,"No."],[4520,4604,"It'll do for now."],[4652,4752,"And for you, sir?"],[4944,5072,"Just water, please."],[5536,5712,"Why so modest? Saving up?"],[5832,5944,"An appetite like yours"],[5944,6128,"would bankrupt Jeff Bezos."],[8020,8264,"Perfect. Bon appétit for me."]],"18":[[5340,5576,"The perfect scandal."]],"19":[[796,916,"Here. Wipe yourself off."],[1148,1468,"Can you be a little more gentle"],[1468,1580,"with your fiancée?"],[1652,1784,"Once you start resembling one."],[1832,1932,"Even just a little."],[2124,2348,"Oh, hey! Where are we going?"],[3600,3720,"Richie?"],[3804,3948,"Richie, baby."],[4528,4672,"I've been waiting for your call."],[4728,4828,"Have you been…"],[4828,5064,"reminiscing on our steamy nights"],[5064,5156,"together?"],[5316,5572,"I have, but I'm not alone."],[5776,5860,"Hi there."]],"20":[[120,240,"Hi there."],[324,556,"Where did you dig her up?"],[556,656,"Who is she?"],[752,976,"She's, uh… my problem."],[1068,1160,"Problem?"],[1160,1288,"Is that what you call"],[1288,1428,"your fiancée, love?"],[1640,1876,"Fiancée? Love?"],[1924,2024,"Yeah."],[2300,2384,"Wait."],[2384,2496,"We've been all over the news."],[2496,2584,"You haven't seen it?"],[2632,2744,"Oh, no."],[2744,2888,"My psychic told me I'd have to take"],[2888,3128,"a vow of abstinence. Forty days."],[3128,3320,"No social media, no news."],[3984,4104,"She's so funny!"],[4168,4288,"You think I'm funny?"],[4288,4464,"Yeah, I think you are."],[4464,4572,"Yeah?"],[4572,4656,"Yeah."],[4656,4740,"You yourself could use"],[4740,4884,"some cleansing too."],[4932,5108,"Dirty outside, dirty inside!"],[5108,5236,"Yeah. Is that"],[5236,5348,"what you want to talk about?"],[5348,5448,"Alright!"],[5448,5560,"Enough, ladies."],[5644,5784,"Felicia, remember?"],[5784,5884,"You're a professional."],[5952,6172,"Fix this disaster quickly."],[6172,6272,"Excuse me?"],[6364,6536,"It wasn't part of a deal."],[6704,6832,"Please."],[7156,7248,"Richard?"]],"21":[[3676,3796,"Babe?"],[3844,3960,"Ta-da!"],[4144,4336,"Ah, shit…"]],"22":[[160,360,"Ah, shit…"],[620,748,"What?"],[748,896,"What the hell is this?"],[896,1016,"I did what I could…"],[1064,1200,"but I'm not a magician."],[1284,1376,"Well, there's no way"],[1376,1496,"I'm showing her to my father"],[1496,1616,"looking like this."],[1616,1700,"But, Richie—"],[1700,1812,"I'll fix this…"],[1944,2044,"by myself."],[2696,2788,"Thank you."],[2788,2940,"Yes, you're right."],[2988,3252,"I think these are the best terms"],[3252,3372,"for our country."],[3372,3464,"Great."],[3512,3612,"Enjoy your meal."],[4152,4252,"Excuse me."],[4656,4776,"The president's son"],[4776,4896,"and his new girlfriend"],[4896,5104,"devour the taxpayers' money."],[5104,5204,"Watch it."],[6956,7084,"Perfect time for a nap?"],[7168,7280,"Maybe I want to sleep too,"],[7280,7424,"but I'm holding it together."],[8072,8164,"Thank God…"],[8220,8396,"I thought you were a lost cause."],[8396,8524,"Well, you should take me"],[8524,8712,"to your girlfriends more often."],[8784,8884,"If it weren't for the money,"],[8884,8996,"I would never let myself"],[8996,9144,"be humiliated like this."],[9792,9960,"My place. Right now."]],"23":[[0,152,"Thank you so much."],[152,252,"My pleasure."],[1300,1452,"Meet our star."],[1532,1668,"Mr. President?"],[1668,1768,"Are you hungry?"],[1840,1940,"No, thanks."],[1940,2024,"Should I make you"],[2024,2200,"five more expensive steaks?"],[2500,2612,"Dad, what's going on?"],[2612,2696,"I was about to ask you"],[2696,2808,"the same question."],[3536,3688,"We were just having dinner and..."],[3772,3888,"and I thought that—"],[4088,4192,"It's—"],[4192,4276,"You know, we—"]],"24":[[768,860,"Guests again?"],[1004,1216,"Okay, fetch me another."],[1372,1468,"Drinking already?"],[1516,1664,"While your son is busy"],[1664,1780,"ruining our lives."],[1844,2028,"First of all, our son."],[2148,2260,"Okay."],[2388,2532,"Okay, what is it about?"],[2744,2976,"Meet Richard's fiancée."],[3436,3536,"I've missed the moment"],[3536,3720,"when our son's taste"],[3720,3856,"changed so drastically."],[4028,4256,"Oh, by the way, nice ring."],[4428,4528,"Quiet."],[4592,4776,"Okay, okay. I'll leave."],[4948,5148,"I'll get the wine by myself."],[5196,5336,"Apologies, daughter-in-law."],[6116,6208,"Dad, listen—"],[6208,6308,"Here."],[6984,7068,"What's this?"],[7068,7228,"Your new apartment."],[7320,7464,"You know exactly where it is."],[7464,7632,"It's in your kind of neighborhood."],[7736,7896,"Now, show my voters"],[7896,8160,"that you're a couple of the people."],[8240,8352,"What about a car?"],[8352,8508,"In that neighborhood,"],[8508,8644,"cars don't last long…"],[8728,8984,"At least, not intact."],[9420,9540,"And if you screw up again…"],[9732,9824,"you will regret it."],[9908,9992,"Both of you."]],"25":[[2448,2576,"This place is a dump."],[3352,3472,"I can get it."],[3636,3756,"Why are you so surprised?"],[3908,4076,"Half of the country lives like this."],[4336,4448,"No, no, no…"],[4592,4776,"No, I refuse to do this."],[4960,5060,"I have to think of something."],[5108,5169,"Yeah, think."],[5193,5384,"I know! We just need money."],[5384,5496,"We'll work and earn it."],[5804,5896,"No."],[5952,6152,"I'm definitely not going to work…"],[6200,6292,"since you made sure"],[6292,6428,"no one will hire me. Remember?"],[6556,6732,"You set those terms yourself."],[7052,7180,"I'll be the housewife."],[7264,7408,"And you can get a side job."],[7520,7728,"Be closer to the people, you know?"],[7728,7864,"I'm a born leader."],[7864,7988,"People work for me,"],[7988,8132,"not the other way around."],[8132,8356,"Yeah, I saw how you \"lead\""],[8356,8476,"in your father's house."]],"26":[[0,228,"Yeah, I saw how you \"lead\""],[228,348,"in your father's house."],[2380,2660,"This is my mother's ring."],[2660,2796,"And I have the right to do with it"],[2796,2888,"as I please."],[3120,3232,"I'll take care of everything."],[3292,3384,"We'll get the money."],[3516,3649,"You're such an idiot."],[3691,3856,"You're done in the neighborhood!"]],"27":[[992,1200,"Sir, are you looking for something?"],[1312,1412,"Yes, thank you."],[1512,1596,"I'm looking for someone"],[1596,1776,"to buy this expensive family heirloom"],[1776,1876,"that I have."],[1924,2024,"I really need some money."],[2652,2772,"I mean, sir…"],[2772,2908,"you've come to the right place."],[2956,3140,"I deal exclusively with jewelry."]],"28":[[0,144,"…you've come to the right place."],[192,376,"I deal exclusively with jewelry."],[460,564,"Really?"],[564,648,"Absolutely. Show me"],[648,748,"what you've got."],[2256,2408,"I mean, fine craftsmanship."],[2456,2608,"I won't even bargain with you."],[2664,2776,"Twenty grand."],[2884,2968,"Twenty grand?"],[2968,3088,"Yes."],[3088,3200,"Deal."],[3292,3496,"And here goes the money."],[3656,3776,"And 20."],[4008,4240,"You idiots! Get out of the way!"],[4240,4472,"The end of the world is near!"],[6776,6952,"The best deal of my life."]],"29":[[212,356,"It was so easy."],[3376,3504,"What are you doing?"],[3504,3680,"Destroying your fantasy world."],[3772,3944,"This is counterfeit."],[4160,4280,"Richard, you're a rich guy."],[4280,4364,"Don't you know"],[4364,4476,"what real money looks like?"],[4540,4660,"I mostly use cards,"],[4660,4812,"and when I've had cash…"],[4880,4992,"I just assumed ATMs"],[4992,5112,"didn't spit out fake ones."],[5208,5308,"Yes, you are."],[5672,5792,"My father was right."],[6464,6592,"I'm a complete idiot."]],"30":[[1172,1356,"We are complete idiots."],[1556,1640,"You're not alone."],[1640,1792,"We're stuck in this together."],[2032,2132,"And you know what?"],[2196,2380,"You're not an idiot at all."],[2480,2944,"You're funny, smart—"],[3040,3124,"Handsome?"],[3240,3340,"Handsome."],[3480,3600,"And a risktaker."],[3872,4032,"You're not afraid to admit…"],[4080,4180,"when you're wrong."],[4392,4632,"You're better than most men."],[5080,5204,"And you—"],[5288,5512,"You can count on me."],[6072,6320,"Y'know, I never heard that before."],[6556,6656,"It's called support."],[6908,7008,"Thank you, Mary."],[7160,7328,"Even if we go our separate ways…"],[7392,7492,"you can count on me too."],[9128,9228,"No…"]],"31":[[364,456,"No…"],[1740,1912,"I'm not much of a housewife."],[1912,2020,"Yeah!"],[2248,2600,"And that was the last of the flour."],[2664,2792,"We're officially out of food."],[3196,3316,"I'm the president's son,"],[3316,3400,"goddammit!"],[3448,3556,"And handsome."],[3556,3704,"Handsome. And smart."],[3796,3888,"Any company would hire me"],[3888,4016,"in a heartbeat."],[4096,4268,"I'll find a job first thing tomorrow."],[4268,4380,"Yeah, do it."],[6564,6660,"Well, sir…"],[6724,6872,"I see your degree…"],[6944,7056,"You're quite accomplished."],[7056,7168,"So, we're agreed?"],[7216,7316,"The position's mine?"],[7472,7580,"No, sir."],[7580,7716,"You have no experience."],[7764,7852,"You telling me that?"],[7900,8012,"Don't you know who I am?"],[8184,8296,"A piece of advice."],[8344,8496,"Start with something simpler."],[8596,8688,"Security!"],[9104,9220,"Next!"],[9348,9460,"No."],[9460,9580,"It's your loss!"],[9808,9892,"Good luck."],[9940,10068,"Wait, wait, wait!"],[10176,10288,"Ah, shit…"],[12340,12440,"No."],[12496,12640,"Why are you asking about this?"],[12688,12800,"We are the best restaurant"],[12800,12892,"in the city."],[12988,13100,"Yes, of course."],[13172,13272,"No."],[13364,13464,"Yes!"],[13664,13764,"Good afternoon, sir."],[13812,13912,"My name's Richard."],[13912,14080,"I saw your sign outside."],[14080,14180,"I don't have much—"],[14372,14456,"You?"]],"32":[[72,176,"You?"],[1056,1192,"I'm the president's son!"],[1192,1320,"And the ring you stole"],[1320,1420,"belongs to the First Lady."],[1520,1652,"Should I call Immigration?"],[1700,1784,"No, no, no."],[1784,1932,"Easy, easy, my friend."],[1980,2132,"Why are you so hot? I think"],[2132,2296,"we misunderstood each other."],[2432,2572,"No, I think I understood perfectly."],[2572,2724,"You gave me fake money."],[2724,2816,"No, I didn't."],[2864,3056,"And the ring is gone. It's gone."],[3120,3392,"Such things sell very fast, y'know?"],[3392,3492,"Yeah? Then give me the money"],[3492,3608,"you made from it."],[3608,3792,"Money? There's no money!"],[3792,3952,"Money gone too."],[3952,4052,"Money gone."],[4052,4252,"I reinvested money in my business."],[4300,4384,"And by the way…"],[4468,4616,"who sells their mother's ring?"],[4836,5104,"What a shame. This is your mother."],[5188,5356,"Well, I'm in a desperate situation."],[5432,5632,"So, what about your father,"],[5632,5776,"the president?"],[5824,5908,"Well, he's the one"],[5908,6008,"who put me here."],[6516,6772,"So, you want to earn some money?"],[6856,7024,"I have a good proposition for you."],[7072,7216,"What? Manage this hole?"],[7496,7580,"Better."],[7912,8056,"Five times better."],[8176,8456,"No! Ten times better."],[9236,9328,"Clean it."]],"33":[[92,184,"Clean it."],[416,516,"Yeah, sure."],[624,776,"Wait, wait, wait!"],[892,976,"Work hard…"],[1024,1176,"and I will bring your ring back."],[1668,1812,"I thought you said you sold it."],[1920,2024,"Don't worry."],[2024,2232,"I have… connections."],[2316,2524,"So, the opening will be soon."],[2824,3048,"And your uniform's on the bag."]],"34":[[684,844,"I will fight you, Richard!"],[1744,1912,"So, how much did I make?"],[2208,2360,"You've made one dollar."],[2612,2712,"What?"],[2712,2856,"I worked enough for three people!"],[2904,3072,"Wait a second. Wait a second."],[3348,3484,"You broke a vase."],[3532,3748,"You left streaks on the floor."],[3868,3952,"Shall I go on?"],[4164,4268,"No."],[4368,4504,"See you tomorrow, my friend."],[4756,4856,"See you tomorrow."],[5008,5108,"You damn fraud."]],"35":[[416,544,"Why even bother with this?"],[668,812,"Vacuum robots exist now."],[812,896,"This is pointless,"],[896,1020,"meaningless work."],[1364,1464,"Okay."],[1556,1668,"Enough whining."],[1880,1976,"Get up!"],[2360,2696,"I'm going to teach you how to mop."],[2804,2952,"You little princess."],[2952,3176,"Princess? My dad made me"],[3176,3304,"earn my own pocket money"],[3304,3440,"since I was 11."],[3440,3600,"I just used my brain to work."],[3600,3816,"Well, I didn't have that privilege."],[3880,4000,"My whole childhood"],[4000,4128,"was just about survival."],[4516,4616,"Alright, smart girl."],[4768,4868,"Teach me."],[4968,5068,"Okay."],[5152,5536,"So, hold my hands tight."],[6708,6988,"Yeah, something like this."],[7104,7280,"More slowly."],[7350,7485,"Slowly."],[7580,7732,"With purpose…"],[7732,7832,"With purpose…"]],"36":[[188,320,"With purpose…"],[320,420,"With purpose…"],[676,844,"I never thought mopping the floor"],[844,944,"would feel this good."],[1108,1208,"Don't rush."],[1960,2096,"Am I imagining things?"],[2096,2288,"Or are you just looking for"],[2288,2432,"an excuse to get closer to me?"],[2496,2608,"Shut up."],[3120,3220,"Your eyes…"],[3388,3532,"I've never noticed them before."],[3748,3848,"They're beautiful."],[4956,5172,"Sorry! Hello."]],"37":[[68,168,"It was open!"],[292,392,"Why?"],[440,540,"Sandy?"],[864,984,"What a dump."],[1436,1556,"I've missed you so much,"],[1556,1684,"my bunny."],[1732,1860,"How did you even find me?"],[1916,2052,"Don't be mad, bunny."],[2100,2212,"I have my contacts."],[2260,2400,"I was worried about you."],[2400,2552,"Yeah? Then why did you disappear"],[2552,2664,"when the scandal broke?"],[2664,2912,"Bunny, my mom's a senator."],[2960,3072,"If I'd stayed with you,"],[3072,3164,"imagine the uproar"],[3164,3264,"it would've caused."],[3264,3364,"And now…"],[3436,3588,"you're not worried"],[3588,3744,"about the uproar?"],[3824,3952,"I'm more worried…"],[4000,4184,"about losing the love of my life."],[4184,4420,"Oh, are you two a couple?"],[4476,4576,"Like, together?"],[4700,4792,"You know? I thought"],[4792,4900,"Richard didn't sleep"],[4900,5044,"with the same girl twice."],[5264,5472,"Richard, where did you find"],[5472,5648,"this hilarious peasant?"],[6300,6496,"Richie and I are together."],[6580,6684,"But you said we were done."],[6756,6848,"That was goodbye sex"],[6848,6944,"back at the shop."],[6992,7292,"Listen, I've changed, okay?"],[7364,7548,"I've had a lot of realizations"],[7548,7632,"since then."],[7632,7732,"I don't think so."],[8048,8224,"People like you don't change"],[8224,8308,"in a week."],[8480,8564,"Richie?"],[8564,8764,"Is she always this exhausting?"],[8944,9044,"Alright."],[9360,9444,"You need a break."],[9516,9812,"I booked us a suite for a few days."],[9860,10060,"No one will find out."]],"38":[[312,412,"Okay."],[504,648,"Call me when you decide."],[1524,1716,"No, you're not going anywhere!"],[1716,1860,"Can't you see she's up to something?"],[1944,2128,"Your father wasted his money"],[2128,2280,"on sending you to Harvard"],[2280,2552,"if you can't see how obvious this is!"],[2600,2780,"I get it! You're in love with me."],[2780,2900,"What?"],[2900,3064,"Where did you get that idea?"],[3064,3220,"I've seen the way you look at me."],[3220,3304,"And those little moments"],[3304,3388,"with the mop."],[3484,3676,"Fine, do whatever you want."],[3676,3796,"I warned you."],[3848,4000,"I'll get my money either way."],[4000,4216,"Yeah, I see it's all you care about."],[4216,4324,"What do you see?"],[4324,4432,"Why don't you even ask"],[4432,4516,"why I need the money?"],[4516,4700,"Why would I? I already know."],[4700,4860,"For a boob job or a nose job."],[4908,5036,"You're just like all the others."],[5304,5552,"Go back to your Sandy."],[5552,5652,"Yeah, I will."],[5756,5924,"And you will regret this."],[6024,6224,"I wish you'd never come into my life!"]],"39":[[244,344,"Damn!"],[492,612,"I might've gone too far."],[1204,1412,"I knew I should've waited for you."],[1900,2000,"Hop in!"],[2648,2800,"You still haven't answered me."],[2800,2936,"How did you know where I was?"],[3176,3276,"Bunny…"],[3332,3492,"Slip a homeless guy a dollar,"],[3492,3644,"and they'll tell you anything."],[3852,4004,"You're a sensation now."],[4116,4292,"The president's son"],[4292,4452,"living among beggars."],[5080,5172,"Haven't you ever thought"],[5172,5316,"that your father might be wrong?"],[5424,5536,"That this beggar scheme"],[5536,5740,"might not be in your best interest?"],[6112,6216,"Don't you think…"],[6288,6408,"Mr. Johnson…"],[6408,6576,"only cares about himself?"],[6864,6992,"Bunny."],[6992,7112,"You deserve a woman"],[7112,7232,"who's worthy of you."],[7304,7448,"Someone you wouldn't be"],[7448,7548,"ashamed of."]],"40":[[192,432,"Sandy, I'm not ashamed of Mary."],[652,772,"Okay."],[992,1112,"Think about it."],[1256,1392,"After your father's election,"],[1392,1492,"you'll break up."],[1668,1844,"He'll still be President, and you?"],[1916,2028,"What kind of reputation"],[2028,2140,"will you have left?"],[2388,2516,"We'll make sure everyone gets"],[2516,2600,"what they want."],[2792,2892,"Yeah."],[3044,3128,"Can't you see"],[3128,3280,"how much you're ruining her life?"],[3372,3508,"She was just a simple…"],[3692,3792,"not too bright…"],[3840,3984,"cleaning girl."],[4120,4328,"She doesn't need all this attention."],[4460,4588,"What did you promise her?"],[4724,4836,"Money?"],[4908,5020,"Yeah."],[5020,5120,"Yeah…"],[5248,5396,"Then convince your father…"],[5444,5584,"she's a bad choice."],[5704,5824,"He'll pay her off."],[5824,6012,"You can go back to your old life."],[6268,6388,"But how?"],[6588,6716,"People need to hate her."],[6972,7164,"Only then will your breakup work"],[7164,7308,"in everyone's favor."],[7552,7664,"Listen to my plan."]],"41":[[48,148,"So?"],[468,552,"What do you think?"],[724,816,"It's harsh,"],[816,1040,"but if you're sure it'll work…"],[1208,1308,"Deal?"],[1804,2052,"Fine. But I need to go to work."],[2196,2292,"Why?"],[2368,2616,"Because I'll be sleeping there today."],[2787,2995,"And I have to pretend nothing's changed."],[3716,3816,"Goodbye."],[5700,5900,"Richard, you're my lucky charm."],[5984,6152,"The profits have doubled."],[6200,6312,"Look what they say in the news."],[6360,6508,"Everybody loves the president"],[6508,6592,"and his son."],[6732,6900,"They say we're close to the people."],[6900,7020,"Yes, yes."],[7268,7460,"You finally did a proper job."],[7700,7800,"Richard."],[7800,7900,"Today, I will pay"],[7900,8028,"a way bigger salary."],[8156,8256,"Three dollars."],[8568,8840,"Yeah. I had a great teacher."],[8964,9316,"Slowly… with purpose…"],[9316,9400,"What?"],[9472,9556,"Nothing."],[9604,9748,"I need to leave early today."],[9812,9932,"Oh, no problem."],[9980,10124,"Clean the second floor,"],[10124,10224,"and you're free."],[12172,12272,"Arrogant jerk."]],"42":[[836,920,"Hello."],[920,1004,"Mary."],[1100,1228,"When should I expect the money?"],[1416,1500,"Mrs. Dora,"],[1500,1612,"you promised me an extension."],[1660,1772,"Circumstances…"],[1772,1864,"have changed."],[1864,2024,"I need the money now."],[2024,2108,"But…"],[2108,2192,"I don't have"],[2192,2312,"that kind of money yet."],[2312,2520,"Then your brother will be placed"],[2520,2780,"with a new family. In fact…"],[2780,2928,"I've already found one."],[2984,3152,"Very influential people…"],[3216,3424,"who've dreamed of having a child."],[3732,3832,"Okay, I'll be there."],[4160,4352,"Richard, please pick up the phone."],[4556,4656,"Richard…"],[4656,4768,"If you're hearing this…"],[4768,4860,"I'm probably in the arms"],[4860,4980,"of another hottie."],[5028,5148,"Leave your boring message"],[5148,5248,"after the beep."],[5296,5396,"Richard, please…"],[5620,5788,"I really need you right now."],[6004,6180,"You promised to be there for me."]],"43":[[0,192,"Max is our star student."],[240,392,"He excels in math, English,"],[392,484,"science, literature—"],[484,636,"you name it. He even—"],[636,764,"Max!"],[764,864,"Mary!"],[1260,1380,"Hi."],[1692,1796,"What are you doing here,"],[1796,1819,"you snake?"],[1854,1938,"Excuse me?"],[1971,2116,"Mind your manners"],[2116,2256,"with a senator's daughter."],[2444,2672,"I'm saving your brother…"],[2724,2892,"despite the fact that you're sleeping"],[2892,2992,"with my boyfriend."],[3040,3124,"That is awful."],[3124,3312,"A child shouldn't be hearing this."],[3312,3404,"Mary!"],[3404,3532,"Max, I'll get back to you!"],[3832,3916,"Why are you lying?"],[3916,4040,"I'm not sleeping with him!"],[4040,4168,"I don't know."],[4380,4480,"He's so…"],[4564,4684,"captivated by you…"],[4828,4874,"What do you want"],[4874,5008,"from me and my brother?"],[5328,5584,"I paid off half of your debt."],[5692,5956,"The rest is just a small favor."],[6224,6360,"You could refuse,"],[6360,6504,"but I wouldn't recommend it."],[6676,6924,"Mrs. Dora told me everything."],[7176,7376,"What do you want?"],[7644,7884,"I want you to set Richard up."]],"44":[[412,556,"You'd do anything for money…"],[684,776,"wouldn't you?"],[1120,1220,"Yes."],[1440,1540,"I'd do anything."],[1824,2040,"But I won't betray Richard."],[2252,2396,"I don't understand."],[2532,2692,"He doesn't value you at all."],[2808,3124,"To him, you're just a cleaner."],[3192,3284,"He only noticed you"],[3284,3520,"'cause of his dad's political games."],[3576,3676,"Maybe you're right…"],[3852,4076,"but Richard is not a bad person."],[4076,4228,"And he doesn't deserve this."],[4420,4520,"How sweet…"],[4640,4740,"Makes me sick."],[4788,4872,"I'll figure out"],[4872,5000,"how to save my brother"],[5000,5084,"on my own."],[5132,5364,"But I'm not getting involved"],[5364,5448,"with you."],[6028,6340,"Foolish girl. You'll regret this."],[7380,7516,"Sir, are you going to order something"],[7516,7700,"besides water? Maybe a steak?"],[8280,8528,"No. I'm waiting for someone."],[8708,8956,"Wait. Do you have a charger?"],[9020,9276,"A charger? Well, I suppose I do."],[9440,9531,"Here you go."],[9531,9616,"Thanks."],[9616,9692,"Yeah, you're welcome."],[9722,10043,"And... maybe, give steak another thought."],[10856,10956,"Richard, please…"],[11064,11232,"I really need you right now."],[11324,11500,"You promised to be there for me."],[11856,12040,"Richard, bunny!"],[12208,12392,"I'm so glad you waited for me."]],"45":[[80,264,"No. I've changed my mind."],[312,448,"I'm telling Mary everything."],[576,802,"She'll understand our plan and play along."],[857,1039,"We don't need to go behind her back."],[1152,1252,"She's sensitive."],[1252,1364,"This would destroy her."],[1460,1612,"I've already gotten out of her"],[1612,1716,"what we needed."],[1848,1960,"You'd do anything for money…"],[1960,2088,"wouldn't you?"],[2088,2208,"Two glasses of wine!"],[2360,2460,"Yes."],[2676,2796,"I'd do anything."],[2892,3012,"Let's publish this."],[3132,3372,"You'll solve all your problems"],[3372,3516,"with one post."],[3616,3784,"Come on, at last."],[3904,4104,"If you don't do it, I will."],[4264,4440,"I'm just worried about you, bunny."],[4592,4692,"Where was this filmed?"],[4776,4888,"It looks familiar…"],[4936,5088,"It's not important."],[5196,5380,"You wouldn't know places like that."],[5472,5680,"Mary's a selfish gold digger, Richie."],[5780,5996,"Remember? She's the one"],[5996,6180,"who leaked you to the press"],[6180,6284,"and humiliated you"],[6284,6428,"in front of your father."]],"46":[[324,416,"What are you doing?"],[500,612,"Richard."],[660,760,"We're meant for each other."],[904,1056,"We were so good together."],[1304,1416,"I've missed you."],[1532,1632,"So?"],[1680,1780,"What do you say?"],[1872,2016,"I deleted it for good."],[2064,2196,"Don't bother checking the bin."],[2428,2716,"Bunny, you did what?"],[2896,3096,"You destroyed such a brilliant plan."],[3096,3208,"I'm done, Sandy."],[3208,3408,"Stop calling me bunny, Richie—"],[3408,3528,"whatever you call me!"],[3528,3620,"C'mon!"],[3620,3748,"Go on, live your life,"],[3748,3860,"and leave me out of it!"],[3860,4036,"I'm sick of all your scheming shit!"],[4144,4384,"Hey! Where are you going?"],[4432,4640,"To Mary. To get the truth."],[5268,5492,"Fine. Go ahead."],[5840,6096,"Good thing I always have a plan B."]],"47":[[56,148,"C'mon. C'mon, Mary."],[148,248,"Please pick up. C'mon."],[448,532,"Ajit?"],[720,848,"Hello?"],[848,948,"Yeah. Yeah."],[1020,1172,"Table six, five, and seven."],[1336,1520,"Plans changed. We are swamped."],[1568,1688,"We need you, Richard."],[1816,1992,"Yeah, sure. I'll be there now."],[2404,2596,"Sir, welcome. Enjoy your dinner."],[2596,2696,"Please, welcome."],[2768,2920,"Oh my God. Oh my God."],[2920,3136,"Richard, Richard, Richard."],[3136,3248,"Something's changed."],[3248,3396,"Are you okay? What's going on?"],[3492,3680,"It's Mary, my fiancée. She—"],[3736,3948,"She's gone. And before that,"],[3948,4060,"she asked me for help."],[4116,4300,"I don't know, Ajit. I screwed up."],[4424,4568,"I let someone close to me down."],[4568,4680,"Okay, hold up."],[4728,4888,"Let's take this step by step, okay?"],[4972,5084,"Where did you see her"],[5084,5184,"the last time?"],[5232,5344,"Back at home. But I checked,"],[5344,5492,"and she's not there."],[5664,5816,"Then someone showed me a video"],[5816,6044,"of her in some weird place."],[6044,6260,"And I don't know where it is."],[6376,6676,"Was there any landmarks or signs?"],[6816,6992,"I don't know. Just something like…"],[7040,7152,"\"sunshine\"."],[7224,7488,"Be the sun… Shine."],[7580,7776,"That's our local orphanage."],[7964,8124,"Ajit, you're the best!"],[8240,8472,"Sorry, I'm taking a day off."],[8472,8632,"Family emergency. Yeah."],[8680,8764,"Okay."],[9152,9436,"Oh boy. I smell trouble."]],"48":[[48,228,"You're in big trouble, young man."],[228,340,"Go back to the classroom!"],[1008,1120,"What an honor."],[1212,1376,"The president's son…"],[1492,1696,"visiting our humble orphanage."],[1696,1848,"Are you here about Max?"],[1896,1996,"Who?"],[2176,2320,"Mary's little brother, of course."],[2320,2420,"There he is."],[2468,2740,"There's a mere $50,000 left to pay."]],"49":[[0,272,"There's a mere $50,000 left to pay."],[892,1116,"I need 50 grand upfront."],[1116,1236,"If it weren't for the money,"],[1236,1348,"I would never let myself"],[1348,1504,"be humiliated like this."],[1504,1628,"Why don't you even ask"],[1628,1728,"why I need the money?"],[1876,1976,"Fifty thousand?"],[2280,2400,"I'm such an idiot…"],[2400,2484,"Would you like to pay"],[2484,2664,"with cash or check?"],[2772,2912,"You see, there's another family"],[2912,3136,"waiting for him. And I must ensure"],[3136,3320,"the guardian's financial stability."],[3376,3624,"Mary is struggling; I'm only doing"],[3624,3808,"what's best for the poor boy."],[4072,4192,"Look. Listen here, lady."],[4240,4392,"I'm not just the president's son."],[4440,4524,"I'm also a lawyer…"],[4572,4684,"which means I know the law."],[4684,4784,"And what you're doing now—"],[4784,4936,"extortion and blackmail—"],[5000,5100,"is a crime."],[5520,5720,"Clearly, you've misunderstood."],[5804,5980,"I was speaking hypothetically."],[6028,6164,"Out of care for Mary"],[6164,6308,"and poor Max."],[6364,6524,"Everything is fine."],[6524,6764,"He can stay as long as necessary."],[6764,6876,"No, I'm not a fool."],[6924,7056,"And I'm not gonna let this slide."],[7236,7476,"Have a nice day, Richard!"],[8196,8308,"Mary, sunshine?"],[8552,8712,"I have so much to say—I dunno."]],"50":[[1664,1816,"Mary, wait. We need to talk."],[1944,2064,"Not now."],[2064,2164,"Right. Not now."],[3228,3364,"I've been dreaming about it…"],[3428,3564,"since we first met."],[3972,4108,"I've been dreaming about this."],[4156,4240,"My breasts?"],[4372,4484,"How predictable."],[4484,4576,"Shut up."],[5228,5488,"Don't ever tell me…"],[5572,5780,"what to do again."],[5892,5992,"You're unbearable."],[8288,8380,"Thank you."],[8572,8672,"Oh, you're welcome."],[8744,8872,"I know I'm amazing in bed."],[8996,9132,"Not for that, idiot."],[9280,9416,"Mrs. Dora called."],[9564,9724,"She said my fiancé…"],[9884,9988,"paid off my debt."],[10124,10260,"I don't know how you found out"],[10260,10388,"about my brother, but…"],[10568,10652,"thank you."],[10960,11276,"No one's ever stood up for me"],[11276,11376,"before."],[11800,11892,"No one's ever gonna hurt you"],[11892,12132,"again. I promise."],[12280,12424,"Your problems will be my problems"],[12424,12624,"now. Got it?"],[12864,12992,"But if you ever keep anything"],[12992,13092,"from me again…"],[13236,13336,"Then what?"],[13336,13456,"Well, then you won't be able to sit"],[13456,13592,"on this gorgeous ass of yours"],[13592,13692,"for a week."],[13860,13952,"Okay."]],"51":[[820,1044,"Richard? Richard, wake up."],[1100,1284,"If I'd known how fiery you were,"],[1284,1468,"I wouldn't've wasted so much time."],[1556,1724,"Well, good morning, lovebirds!"],[1724,1920,"Dad? What are you doing here?"],[1968,2204,"Me? Fixing the consequences"],[2204,2428,"of trusting you. Recognize this?"],[2784,2996,"No, Dad. You've got it all wrong."],[3044,3152,"She made the move."],[3152,3252,"Really?"],[3252,3368,"I promise this won't affect"],[3368,3452,"your ratings."],[3452,3684,"I'm tired of constantly worrying"],[3684,3868,"about how you will affect"],[3868,4000,"my ratings."],[4112,4236,"You're beyond fixing."],[4320,4432,"Dad, what are you up to?"],[4540,4632,"I'm still here."],[4784,4912,"Can someone explain to me"],[4912,5024,"what's going on here?"],[5024,5280,"And what's this photo about?"],[5328,5484,"Mary, not now."],[5576,5792,"So, I'm just invisible here."],[5876,6084,"Okay, I've had enough."],[6724,6908,"Mary? Mary?"],[6956,7120,"It's working. Come in!"],[7176,7260,"Dad, what are you—"],[8380,8480,"My son got involved"],[8480,8608,"with a drug addict"],[8608,8752,"and became an addict himself."],[8752,8864,"Such a poor boy."],[9020,9180,"I'll have to send him to rehab."],[9404,9536,"Yeah, I'm not proud of myself"],[9536,9636,"as a father…"],[9744,9856,"but I'll do everything"],[9856,9996,"to be a president…"],[9996,10116,"worthy of this country."],[10180,10320,"My condolences, sir."],[10404,10504,"But…"],[10616,10744,"great speech."],[10896,10996,"Wrote it last night."],[11104,11188,"Grab them."],[11400,11500,"And then…"],[11500,11700,"I'll have one more task for you."]],"52":[[1332,1389,"What the hell are you doing? Give it back."],[1390,1465,"Give it back."],[1465,1580,"Did they give you permission"],[1580,1692,"to take a photo of them?"],[1740,1944,"What? Listen, your ugly accent—"],[1944,2032,"I don't understand"],[2046,2200,"even a word you're saying."],[2200,2388,"Listen, honey. Go eat some…"],[2520,2640,"curry and butter chicken"],[2640,2752,"or whatever."],[2800,2960,"Give it back just right now, okay?"],[3008,3100,"This is a crime…"],[3184,3364,"to say such ugly words…"],[3364,3540,"from such a beautiful mouth."],[3612,3740,"Total freak. Okay, fine."],[3740,3852,"That's my gift."],[3852,4060,"No camera, then my phone will do this."],[5564,5924,"What are you doing here?"],[6024,6168,"I was looking for Richard."],[6252,6344,"This is the first day"],[6344,6488,"he didn't come at his work."],[6656,6776,"Listen…"],[6824,7092,"Honey, you don't even know"],[7092,7252,"who you are messing with, okay?"],[7252,7404,"I'm the best journalist in the city."],[7404,7524,"And you have a problem."],[7580,7812,"Hand over my stuff. Now."],[7812,7912,"Okay."],[8104,8204,"Are you crazy?"],[8256,8352,"No worries, baby girl."],[8352,8464,"I will buy you a new one."],[8572,8672,"And by the way…"],[8756,8840,"Hey!"],[8932,9192,"As for this, you will get it back"],[9192,9304,"on our first date."],[9420,9604,"Our first date? Really?"],[9712,9864,"Are you out of your mind completely?"],[9864,9976,"Give it back, I said."],[10208,10424,"Date? You just said date?"],[10424,10508,"Listen, honey."],[10508,10696,"In 1,000,000 years, no."],[10900,11156,"Deal. My café. Tonight."],[11452,11572,"What café?"],[11956,12056,"You are the best journalist"],[12056,12140,"in the city."],[12140,12224,"For sure."],[12272,12384,"Find out."],[12448,12532,"Pardon."],[12588,12672,"What?"],[12952,13052,"Hey!"],[13152,13336,"Hey, pretty lady."],[13336,13420,"What are you doing"],[13420,13504,"in our part of town?"],[13504,13604,"Hey, hey, hey! Back off!"],[13672,13756,"Wait a minute."],[13852,13952,"Where did you get that?"]],"53":[[300,468,"Wasn't there a second blanket?"],[560,752,"I don't want to sit next to him."],[1636,1776,"Mary, you've got it all wrong."],[1860,2152,"Oh, right. I'm just a dumb…"],[2224,2408,"blind cleaning lady"],[2408,2528,"who's good enough to use"],[2528,2676,"for your political games, right?"],[2776,2888,"Drink."],[3172,3364,"I'm not drinking this."],[3364,3580,"If you want to feel better, drink."],[3824,3952,"Let him drink it first."],[4020,4208,"I wouldn't mind if it poisoned him."],[4316,4580,"Fine. It's just tea."],[5976,6160,"Now, I'll never drink this."],[6252,6460,"If you don't drink it willingly,"],[6460,6724,"I will help you with that. Drink."],[6868,7140,"Okay. Come on, darling! Drink it."],[7140,7360,"It will help you. Drink it. Drink."]],"54":[[256,408,"Here's the surprise. I know"],[408,536,"you stole the First Lady's ring."],[536,772,"That's mine. I lost it."],[892,1100,"It was stolen from you. I know that."],[1148,1300,"Those two homeless guys told me."],[1300,1432,"The ones you sent after me."],[1432,1532,"Bring it back."],[1592,1704,"The phone for the ring."],[1752,1872,"Remember? We had a deal."],[1956,2148,"Our date. So, I'm here."],[2148,2324,"This is our date. Let it be."],[2324,2424,"Okay."],[2424,2680,"I took a couple of photos. Enjoy."],[2752,2836,"I can handle it."],[3100,3200,"What's happening?"]],"55":[[236,340,"What's happening?"],[724,872,"You lied to me this whole time?"],[872,1028,"Richard, my friend, I—"],[1028,1128,"You're no friend of mine."],[1252,1364,"And what's she doing here?"],[1896,2088,"Excuse me? What am I doing here?"],[2144,2320,"I'm actually doing my job, okay?"],[2368,2468,"What job?"],[2552,2636,"All you ever do is"],[2636,2760,"ruin other people's lives."],[2808,3168,"Well, it's much better to ruin lives"],[3168,3408,"than to be a little spoiled boy"],[3408,3508,"who can't stand up to"],[3508,3668,"his overbearing daddy"],[3668,3788,"at 25 years old."],[3788,3880,"Elizabeth, chill!"],[3880,4060,"Who's talking here?"],[4060,4296,"The king of con artists, right?"],[4296,4496,"I know everything about you too."],[4544,4780,"And how you funded this tiny café."],[4828,5012,"Listen, just 'cause you rob the rich,"],[5012,5124,"it doesn't make you Robin Hood."],[5280,5480,"You guys all make me sick."],[5480,5592,"Thank God I don't just work"],[5592,5692,"for Michael Johnson."],[5692,5952,"I also work for your ex, Sandy."],[5952,6052,"Yeah, yeah."],[6332,6524,"Now, she's a proper client."],[6524,6624,"Surprised?"],[6684,6796,"What does Sandy have to do"],[6796,6900,"with this?"],[6948,7068,"Even dumber than I thought."],[7184,7320,"Her mother is planning"],[7320,7488,"to run for president."],[7544,7628,"Oh!"],[7712,7864,"You look so sad and surprised."],[7948,8048,"Do you really think that"],[8048,8148,"she's choosing you just"],[8148,8452,"because of big, huge, true love?"],[8452,8572,"No, honey."],[8572,8748,"She's doing absolutely everything"],[8748,8832,"to take down"],[8832,8976,"her mother's biggest competition."],[9024,9168,"And it's your father."],[9168,9268,"And that is the truth."]],"56":[[48,148,"And that's my job."],[284,384,"You know?"],[448,664,"I even feel sorry for you, Richard."],[712,856,"It seems to be so sad…"],[928,1112,"to be all your life, just a puppet"],[1112,1280,"in someone else's political games."],[1280,1372,"But that's life."],[1372,1564,"That's what all the people say."],[1564,1764,"And I'm gonna say good luck…"],[1888,1972,"bunny loser."],[1972,2156,"Elizabeth. Elizabeth, wait."],[2364,2464,"As I promised."],[3164,3316,"I warned you about Sandy."],[3388,3472,"But why would the words…"],[3472,3632,"of a dumb cleaning lady matter?"],[3632,3732,"Stop it!"]],"57":[[132,284,"I warned you about Sandy."],[356,440,"But why would the words…"],[440,600,"of a dumb cleaning lady matter?"],[600,700,"Stop it!"],[968,1060,"Mary…"],[1060,1204,"Don't be so hard on yourself."],[1452,1656,"I would never fall in love with you"],[1656,1756,"if you were just some…"],[1756,1868,"dumb cleaning lady."],[2288,2400,"What did you just say?"],[2680,2800,"You love me?"],[3032,3132,"Yeah."],[3180,3388,"It actually scares me how much."],[3688,3864,"I feel like, without you, I—"],[3972,4064,"I was never whole…"],[4268,4412,"never truly myself."],[4608,4708,"Mary."],[4852,4936,"You're the best thing"],[4936,5056,"that's ever happened to me."],[5220,5304,"And I'm sorry,"],[5304,5536,"but I'm never letting you go."],[7956,8076,"This is the happiest moment"],[8076,8168,"of my life."],[8300,8492,"And I can't even enjoy it"],[8492,8648,"'cause my brother could be taken"],[8648,8744,"any time."],[9048,9232,"Look, I know"],[9232,9360,"I've been a complete idiot…"],[9644,9812,"I know how to save your brother."],[10612,10712,"Richard?"],[11340,11440,"Maybe we shouldn't."],[11504,11632,"We're not criminals."]],"58":[[552,652,"Richard?"],[1280,1380,"Maybe we shouldn't."],[1444,1572,"We're not criminals."],[1656,1796,"I'm stealing from myself."],[1984,2096,"A few years back,"],[2096,2208,"I made a great investment"],[2208,2320,"in a startup."],[2320,2528,"Then my dad asked for my money"],[2528,2640,"to fund his campaign."],[2748,2896,"And he never gave it back."],[2968,3148,"Said it was the price"],[3148,3348,"for my first 18 years of life."],[3480,3672,"So now… we'll take $100K…"],[3720,3820,"for our new life…"],[3876,3960,"even though I made"],[3960,4044,"100 times more."],[5216,5368,"Damn, he changed the code."]],"59":[[308,392,"Do you really think"],[392,520,"your father is an idiot?"],[568,652,"And he will let you"],[652,736,"take all his money"],[736,836,"just like that?"],[836,920,"Mom, you know"],[920,1040,"that's my money sitting there."],[1088,1184,"I just never had the guts"],[1184,1304,"to take it back."],[1304,1656,"I know, my sweetheart. I know,"],[1656,1944,"but Michael doesn't see it like that."],[1992,2176,"You're nothing like your father."],[2240,2488,"And that's always driven him crazy."],[2916,3100,"Is this for you or for—"],[3184,3284,"What's your name again?"],[3344,3456,"Mary."],[3596,3696,"For us."],[4256,4356,"Do you realize"],[4356,4508,"that there's no going back"],[4508,4600,"and Michael will know"],[4600,4700,"who stole his money?"],[4700,4820,"Yeah, because I'm the cause"],[4820,4912,"of all his problems."],[4960,5044,"I told Michael"],[5044,5276,"that he underestimated you."],[5392,5492,"But Mommy…"],[5492,5668,"always believed in you."],[5824,5920,"Stand back."],[9964,10064,"Mom, come with us."],[10148,10232,"Dad's gonna lose it"],[10232,10360,"when he finds out what you did."],[10468,10716,"No. My life is here."],[11116,11300,"And I will not leave your father."],[11492,11592,"Cheers."],[12024,12124,"Let's get outta here."],[12404,12504,"Not so fast, son."]],"60":[[72,240,"Not so fast, son."],[240,384,"That's what I expected from you."],[1192,1336,"I've dreamed of doing that"],[1336,1436,"for years."],[1832,1932,"Why are you standing around?"],[2064,2184,"Richard, check the pulse."],[2668,2796,"He'll be fine."],[2796,3052,"This man will outlive all of us."],[3144,3288,"And now, get out."],[3596,3708,"Thank you, Mrs. Johnson."],[4144,4244,"Honey?"],[4464,4556,"Honey?"],[4636,4736,"Honey?"],[5012,5112,"Hey…"],[5380,5480,"Okay."],[5544,5796,"Honey, it's time to let go of…"],[5796,6020,"your power-hungry ambitions."],[6076,6212,"You have had your fun."],[6264,6408,"Enough is enough."],[6408,6512,"But—"],[6512,6612,"No buts."],[6736,6872,"Or I'll leave you."],[7020,7172,"But I did it for us."],[7288,7424,"For you. You always wanted"],[7424,7544,"to be First Lady."],[7688,7788,"I remember."],[7996,8096,"But I was wrong."],[8200,8300,"Really?"],[9328,9456,"I miss the old us."],[9628,9756,"Me too."],[10460,10560,"Does it hurt?"],[10608,10708,"Yeah, it does."],[10756,10856,"Okay."],[10856,11032,"Okay? You're crazy."],[11032,11132,"Yeah."]],"61":[[312,624,"Max? Stop eating so much."],[624,712,"Just one, please."],[844,944,"Okay."],[1228,1312,"And now you can go."],[1360,1504,"Such a strict woman."],[1568,1680,"It really turns me on."],[1948,2068,"Shush. Guests."],[2152,2244,"Dad, hey!"],[2244,2604,"Hey. This is for our granddaughter."],[2652,2744,"Or grandson."],[2744,2840,"No."],[2888,3000,"We don't know yet."],[3000,3096,"Okay, okay…"],[3768,3956,"I still can't believe you forgave me."],[4124,4308,"Power corrupted me so much"],[4308,4448,"that I forgot who I truly was."],[4616,4728,"Mary."],[4828,5020,"Thank you for coming into our lives."],[5092,5192,"Yeah."],[5492,5744,"So? Sandy won?"],[5844,6036,"Her mother's leading the race…"],[6164,6364,"now that you've stepped down."],[6412,6580,"No, she's trapped herself…"],[6664,6764,"and just doesn't know it yet."],[7196,7348,"I almost caught them."],[7348,7448,"And guess what happened next?"],[7448,7532,"What?"],[7532,7712,"They just vanished like crazy elves."],[7712,7812,"Darling."],[7876,8028,"Finally! Late, as always."],[8124,8208,"You know my wife."],[8208,8328,"She's chasing some scoop,"],[8328,8440,"a new sensation…"],[8488,8584,"and almost missed"],[8584,8736,"the most important one."],[8736,8960,"It drives me crazy. Like, always."],[8960,9044,"Okay."],[9092,9228,"We are so glad to be here."],[9228,9376,"And my dear friends…"],[9376,9504,"congratulations."],[9760,9852,"Mr. President."],[9956,10040,"Darling, I'm so thirsty."],[10040,10152,"I'm gonna get us drinks."],[10152,10248,"I'm gonna help you."],[10408,10508,"You're so beautiful."],[10864,11048,"What are we gossiping about?"],[11096,11196,"About…"],[11288,11444,"how wonderful it is"],[11444,11640,"that we're all here together."],[12620,12720,"And it's all thanks to you."],[12900,13004,"Alright. Come on."],[13004,13120,"Let's find out who's in there."],[13420,13520,"Wait. Wait for us."],[13616,13744,"It's your personal journalist here."],[13744,13856,"Okay?"],[13944,14040,"So?"],[14040,14152,"Let's count."],[14152,14260,"Are you ready?"],[14260,14368,"Yeah."],[14368,14516,"Three! Two!"],[14516,14616,"One!"],[14996,15132,"Congratulations!"],[15544,15720,"So, this was Elizabeth Skeeter"],[15720,15840,"for Breaking News Live."],[15840,16000,"It was so interesting."],[16000,16116,"Stay with us, babies."]]}